Text:
100 Wayz is the seventh studio album by Tha Dogg Pound. It was originally scheduled 
to be released after their 2007 release, Dogg Chit. Their seventh album, That Was 
Then This Is Now was released instead. 100 Wayz is to be released on August 17, 2010 
but Amazon.com put it up for pre-order sale three weeks earlier on July 27, 2010...
